Employee{id=&#39;100&#39;, name=&#39;Alex&#39;, city=&#39;Atlanta&#39;}
Employee{id=&#39;200&#39;, name=&#39;Rida&#39;, city=&#39;null&#39;}
Employee{id=&#39;300&#39;, name=&#39;Ganga&#39;, city=&#39;Boston&#39;}
Employee{id=&#39;400&#39;, name=&#39;null&#39;, city=&#39;Pleasanton&#39;}
```

